ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#54: FILE: mm/swapfile.c:1639:
+		if (!(p->swap_map = __alloc_vcompound(GFP_KERNEL | __GFP_ZERO,

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

